title: Bliss Cafe & Patisserie
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Delivery, Take-out, British, Catering, English, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A clean cafe with a pleasant atmosphere. As of early 2016, has these vegan hot dishes on the menu: Morrocan tagine, lasagne, chickpea curry and chilli, all of which are made-in-house using quality local ingredients. Staff happy to accommodate vegans. Available for take-away also. Has gluten free choices. Wi-Fi. Dog & child friendly.
